Naruto-AI-Tweets/
│
├── ai/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── tweet_generator.py       # AI model to generate tweets for different clans
│   ├── personality_model.py     # Machine learning model to train AI on clan personalities
│   └── data_preprocessor.py     # Preprocess text data for AI training
│
├── scripts/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── tweet_bot.py            # Automated bot that tweets using the generated AI text
│   ├── train_model.py          # Training script for the AI model
│   └── deploy_twitter_bot.py   # Script to connect to Twitter and deploy the bot
│
├── tests/
│   ├── test_tweet_generator.py  # Unit tests for tweet generation
│   └── test_personality_model.py # Tests for training and personality modeling
│
├── requirements.txt            # Python dependencies
├── config.json                 # Configuration file for Twitter API and other settings
├── LICENSE.md                  # Project license
└── README.md                   # Project documentation
